export const semver=/^[v^~<>=]*?(\d+)(?:\.([x*]|\d+)(?:\.([x*]|\d+)(?:\.([x*]|\d+))?(?:-([\da-z\-]+(?:\.[\da-z\-]+)*))?(?:\+[\da-z\-]+(?:\.[\da-z\-]+)*)?)?)?$/i;export const validateAndParse=r=>{if("string"!=typeof r)throw new TypeError("Invalid argument expected string");const e=r.match(semver);if(!e)throw new Error(`Invalid argument not valid semver ('${r}' received)`);return e.shift(),e};const isWildcard=r=>"*"===r||"x"===r||"X"===r,tryParse=r=>{const e=parseInt(r,10);return isNaN(e)?r:e},forceType=(r,e)=>typeof r!=typeof e?[String(r),String(e)]:[r,e],compareStrings=(r,e)=>{if(isWildcard(r)||isWildcard(e))return 0;const[t,n]=forceType(tryParse(r),tryParse(e));return t>n?1:t<n?-1:0};export const compareSegments=(r,e)=>{for(let t=0;t<Math.max(r.length,e.length);t++){const n=compareStrings(r[t]||"0",e[t]||"0");if(0!==n)return n}return 0};